edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits

Class MixModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits.MixModel

  • public class MixModel
extends Object
    This class represents a Mix object, with various convenient functions for use by XmlContentConverter in building up the structure. It's a captive class with no public interface, so data fields are directly accessible.
